<br>
Before SCS3, I alternated <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Boots of Bladecalling</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> with <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Wrath of Elements</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, with an occasional real nuke.  I used the mage dot because it is low aggro.<br>
<br>
But with <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>SCS3</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> I could alternate boots and rains instead of dots, and hardly ever take aggro from my pet.<br>
<br>
I find the ability worth it, but it does make aggro kiting harder.<br>
